      <pattern name="Ribbon launcher delegation" location="src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/ribbon/EntityFormLaunch.ts">Ribbon scripts are invocation-only; all URL/business logic lives in `launch-resolver.ts` (ADR-006).</pattern>
